data.description: From the moment you walk through the door you will notice the spacious living room, sizable kitchen and eating area. The main bedroom has a wonderfully sized closet and en suite bath. The remaining bedrooms are large and include generous closet space. The exterior is charming and classic with 4 side brick which is easily maintained over the years.  This home is only missing one thing. Call to schedule a showing before its. SOLD!
